      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROLLING ROYALTY (7) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a P5 at this track. Can make amends this time. TWO FACED GWEN (8) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (20.10) but scored four back at Q Lakeside (22.05). Must be included in calculations. WIGGLE ON (1) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 6th at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Has a strong record from this draw. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and a minor placing from seven starts. Cannot be taken lightly. CURIOUS CAZA (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
